verbose_text: In addition to activating proteolysis, TWEAK also up-regulates the expression of matrix metalloproteinases (MMPs), especially MMP-9, which may be responsible for extracellular matrix breakdown and fibrosis in atrophying skeletal muscle [XREF_BIBR].
